</span><a href=\"#/articles/course/AptitudeCourses/gfg-sub-aptitude/aptitude/simplification-and-approximation-solved-questions-and-answers/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><span>Solved Questions</span></a><span> | </span><a href=\"#/articles/course/AptitudeCourses/gfg-sub-aptitude/quizzes/simplification-and-approximation-gq/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><span>Quiz</span></a></li><li value=\"28\"><a href=\"#/articles/course/AptitudeCourses/gfg-sub-aptitude/aptitude/data-interpretation-1/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><b><strong>Data Interpretation</strong></b></a><span>\u00a0|\u00a0</span><a href=\"#/articles/course/AptitudeCourses/gfg-sub-aptitude/aptitude/data-interpretation-questions-aptitude/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><span>Solved Questions</span></a><span>\u00a0| </span><a href=\"#/articles/course/AptitudeCourses/gfg-sub-aptitude/quizzes/data-interpretation-gq/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><span>Quiz</span></a></li></ul><h2 id=\"logical-reasoning-topics\" style=\"text-align:left\"><span>Logical Reasoning Topics</span></h2><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>Logical Reasoning covers a wide range of topics and questions, including:-</span></p><ul><li value=\"1\"><a href=\"#/articles/course/AptitudeCourses/gfg-sub-aptitude/aptitude/number-series-in-quantitative-aptitude/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><b><strong>Number Series</strong></b></a><b><strong> </strong></b><span>| </span><a href=\"#/articles/course/AptitudeCourses/gfg-sub-aptitude/aptitude/number-series-solved-questions-and-answers/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><span>Solved Questions</span></a><span> | </span><a href=\"#/articles/course/AptitudeCourses/gfg-sub-aptitude/quizzes/series-gq/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><span>Quiz</span></a></li><li value=\"2\"><a href=\"#/articles/course/AptitudeCourses/gfg-sub-aptitude/aptitude/alphanumeric-series/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><b><strong>Letter and Symbol Series</strong></b